      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a dependable choice for daily transportation. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car starts reliably, potential buyers should be aware of some minor oil seepage and a suspension that is beginning to feel its age. The exterior shows some noticeable cosmetic wear and the interior has seen better days, but all essential safety features and electronics are in working order. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
